quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  2,6,"Zvirokwazvo, avo vasingatendi, zvimwe chete kwavari (iwe Muhammad (SAW)) kuvayambira kana kusavayambira, havafi vakatenda"
  2,7,"Allah vakavhara moyo yavo nenzeve dzavo (havatambiri gwara raAllah), uye maziso avo akafukidzwa (mukuona chokwadi); uyezve vachawana mutongo wakaomarara"
  2,8,"Muvanhu mune vamwe (vanyengedzi) vanoti: “Tinotenda muna Allah nezuva rekupedzisira,” asi muchokwadi havatendi"
  2,9,"Vanofunga kuti vanonyengedza Allah nevanotenda, asi zvirokwazvo vanozvinyengedza pachavo, uye havazvioni"
  2,10,Mumoyo yavo mune chirwere (kusagutsikana nehunyengedzi) uye Allah vanowedzera chirwere chavo; uye vachava nemutongo unorwadza nokuti vaigaro nyepa
  2,11,"Uye vakaudzwa kuti: “Musava munoita zvisakarurama munyika,” vanoti: “Zvirokwazvo, tiri vachengetedzi verunyararo (tiri vanhu vanoita mabasa akarurama).”"
  2,12,"Zvirokwazvo, ndivo vaiti vezvisakarurama, asi havazvioni"
  2,13,"Uye zvikanzi kwavari: “Tendai sekutenda kwakaitwa nevanhu (vateveri vaMuhammad (SAW)),” vanoti: “Tingatenda here sekutenda kwakaita vanhu vasina njere (vakapusa)?” Zvirokwazvo, ndivo vasina njere, asi havazvizivi"
  2,14,"Uye pavanosangana nevatendi, vanoti: “Tiri vatendi,” asi kana vave voga nevanyengedzi vavo, vanoti: “Zvirokwazvo, tinemi; zvirokwazvo, tanga tichingovatsvinyira.”"
  2,15,Allah vanovatsvinyira uyezve vanovawedzera mabasa avo akaipa kuti vave vanotekaira vasingaoni
  2,16,Ndeavo (vanoshandura) vanotsvaga kurasika vachisiya gwara nekudaro hapana chavakawana pakutsvaga kwavo; uye havana kutungamirirwa